quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  43,34,"(Min mba…óayno kadi) e cuu…ói ma…ď…ďe …óiin, dame e nda…ó…óude ka …ďe so…ď…ďindoo,"
  43,35,"e cu…óaari. Kono …óuum fow wonaani, si wonaa dakamme nguurndam aduna. Ko La'akara on ka Joomi maa, woni fii gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen."
  43,36,"Kala …óuurnii…óo e jaŇčtoore Hinaranko On, Min nguurta mo e seytanuuru, hara ko ndun woni ko o coowodata."
  43,37,"∆äiin (awaseeji) noon, ko sakkoray…ói …ďe e peewal ngal, haa ka …ďe cikkata hi…ďe peewi."
  43,38,"Haa si o aroyii e Amin, o wi'a: "Ee bone ! hara hakkunde am e maa wo…ó…óirayno go…ó…óal pu…ó…óir…óe …óen …ói…ói wo…ó…óiri ! A bonii cinndadii…óo !"."
  43,39,"[∆äuum] nafataa on hannde - nde tawnoo on too√Īii - won'de ko ka lepte kaawtu…óon."
  43,40,"E ko an naninta paa…óu…óo maa feewnaa bun…óo e on won…óo e ndeer majjere …ďanngunde?"
  43,41,"Si Min ngar ∆īettitude ma, ko Min yo…ďottotoo…ďe e ma…ď…ďe."
  43,42,"maa hara Men holle ko Min kammbirani …ďeen kon, haray noon ko Min gaynoo…ďe fii ma…ď…ďe."
  43,43,"Jogito kon ko wahayinaa e maa…óa. Pellet, hi…óa jokki laawol pocciingol."
  43,44,"Ndee non [Alqur'aanaare], ko nde teddungal maa an e yim…ďe maa …ďeen. Aray nde la…ďnditee…óon."
  43,45,"Lamndii e …ďeen Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďe Min nulunoo ado maa, si Min mba…óuno ko wanaa Hinnaranke On, dewetee…ói goo?"
  43,46,"GooŇč…óii Min immindinii Muusaa e aayeeje Amen …óeen, haa e Fir'awna e mbatu mun ngun, o maaki: "Ko mi Nulaa…óo Jey…óo tagoore"."
  43,47,"Nde o addannoo…ďe aayeeje Amen …óren, e jaka yoo hi…ďe njala…ói."